<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.6">
<l>erutuka ḷōṭu poruti yētumu lōpāykā ṉampi</l>
<l>karutiya tīmaikaḷ ceytu kañcaṉaik kālkoṭu pāyntāy.</l>
<l>teruviṉkaṇ tīmaikaḷ ceytu cikkeṉa mallarka ḷōṭu</l>
<l>porutu varukiṉṟa poṉṉē puṉṉaippūc cūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Prince! Look! Since fighting the oxen,</l>
<l rend="indent">you want for nothing at all.</l>
<l>You who, causing the mischief [you] intended,</l>
<l rend="indent">lept [and grabbed] Kaṃsa by the leg,</l>
<l>Golden one who, creating mischief in the streets,</l>
<l rend="indent">came along tenaciously to fight the wrestlers,</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] adorn [you] with Puṉṉai blossoms!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
